{"books":[{"id":"whb","name":"文汇报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"百万颗红心向太阳","authors":["陈忠干"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":8,"day":21}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"上海警备区　陈忠干"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席穿上布军装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天刚破晓就来到了天安门广场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会见百万革命群众。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百万颗红心向太阳!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席伸出伟大的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使文化革命高潮一涨再涨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席发出的伟大号召，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每句话都说在我们心坎上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们一定要关心国家大事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们一定要把无产阶级文化大革命进行到底!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们步步跟着毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去见世面，去破风浪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一手猛挥笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一手紧握枪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢去打头阵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢去打硬仗!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢把一切牛鬼蛇神都扫光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢把旧世界彻底埋葬!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让毛泽东思想伟大红旗千秋万代发红光!"}],"comments":[],"origin":"","comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}